####更新map中的值
```scala
import scala.collection.mutable.Map
val b = Map(1->"abc",2->"c")
b(1) = "ccc"
b(1) //ccc
```

#####添加元素到map中
```scala
import scala.collection.mutable.Map
val b = Map(1->"abc",2->"c")
b +=(3->"c")
```

#####移除某个元素
```scala
import scala.collection.mutable.Map
val b = Map(1->"abc",2->"c")
 b-= 1
```